p: Between MM_FP and ww_FP, targeted genes for DE lncRNAs were enriched, the terms were related to regulation of protein complex assembly and biogenesis, protein complex subunit organization, spindle assembly involved in mitosis process. DE mRNAs were most enriched, the meaningful terms were related to regulation of secondary metabolic and biosynthetic process, viral protein processing, single-organism biosynthetic process (Fig. 3b, Supplementary material 5B, 6B).
